## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on publicly available opinions and may not fully represent the diversity of perspectives on this issue. Additionally, the sources used are primarily from online platforms, which may introduce bias based on the demographics of their user base. Further research, including academic studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.